--- !u!114 &241488873
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 241488872}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: dab40134f96b0c04e893ef68ca62f8c8, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GameManager01
  dialogue_text01: {fileID: 1658181777}
  character_text01: {fileID: 1185008129}
  dialogue01:
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "Regardless, I\u2019ve also been too engrossed in my research
      to really even THINK about interacting with other people."
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: What are your goals when it comes to your research?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "Well, I want to prove that creatures like you exist\u2026"
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: But why does it matter so much to you whether you do or do not?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: (Huh, good question)
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "\u2026I guess I just want everyone to see how beautiful they
      are. We live in a world where people kinda lost all their whimsy\u2026"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "We\u2019re too focused on being serious, uhm, I think?"
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: How so?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "I mean, there\u2019s always pressure to make money, or perform
      well, or make the best use of your time. People forget to slow down. We\u2019ve
      started referring to time as a commodity and not for what it really is\u2026"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: The means for us to measure our existences and make the most of
      it.
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: You are very cute.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: I- huh?
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: 'I think it is endearing that your motives are to do with the
      improvement of how other people view their lives. '
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: It is common here in Japan that you must work hard or else you
      are wasting your time. But how can one waste their time if they are still living?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "Yeah\u2026yeah\u2026"
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: ...
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ...
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Sorry, did I get too philosophical?
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: 'No, not at all, I have plenty of time to think of these topics
      since I live so far from others. Though it is nice to have someone to share
      it with. '
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "Ah, I\u2019m glad. You\u2019re nice to talk to."
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: 'Oh! I- uhm- Ahem. '
    options: []
  - char_name: Akira
    dialogue_text: Thank you. Same goes for you.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: 'I appreciate it. '
    options: []
  line_index01: 0
